{
  "stem": "8784.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But thank god he was not the same commander, and he had no influence on our lives anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It does set you back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- you-- you swallow and-- and wonder, I mean, are we going backwards, or is the clock still moving into the right direction?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is no question, but it sort of makes you wonder.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in Brunnlitz itself, yes, we had the luxury of talking to one another.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The great fear of the concentration camp was dissipating slowly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not a total free-for-all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't go around the whole camp and shake hands with all the inmates in the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I couldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, if I could've, I would've found out if there was another Urbach by the name of David, first name.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But on the other hand, I developed [? many other ?] friendships with people my age.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I became very close friends with a-- with people that worked together with me in the workshop.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And some of the entries that were made in my memoir when the-- when the war ended tell the story of how we felt towards-- how these people felt towards me.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the particular friendship that I developed was with a girl by the name of Anita Lampel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You could not call it a girlfriend-boyfriend, but we were certainly on a talking-- in a talking relationship, friendly with one another.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Olek Allerhand, who was in Israel; Anita Lampel, who was-- later on remained in Poland, educated herself, and then eventually migrated to Israel, lived in Israel, now deceased; Adel Mandel he was to-- who was described by me before, but did not survive in Brunnlitz, also deceased.",
      "word_count": 47
    }
  ],
